                        <interp inst="t18370403-1058-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 62.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy.</hi>—
<rs id="t18370403-1058-punishment-125" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18370403-1058-punishment-125" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
