                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1058-18370403 t18370403-1058-punishment-125"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Coleridge.</hi>
